{"tid":2188161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文晤捷議長：公理正義不會不到  游錫堃受邀回訪 促議會交流","createTime":"2020-09-04T05:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T05:45:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db3df0ef60361b4b7c6374612a77170e69e57994","tid":2188161,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200904/KHJMRMMBSFGYJP7UN3U52LIASI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200904%2FKHJMRMMBSFGYJP7UN3U52LIASI%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=58f765f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200904%2FKHJMRMMBSFGYJP7UN3U52LIASI%2F&h=acd5f778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200904/KHJMRMMBSFGYJP7UN3U52LIASI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文晤捷議長：公理正義不會不到 <br />\n游錫堃受邀回訪 促議會交流<br />\n<br />\n【共抗威權】捷克參議院議長維特齊率團訪台接近尾聲，昨與台灣總統蔡英文會晤。蔡致辭時說，很遺憾生前計劃訪台的參議院前議長柯佳洛未能到訪，但稱不介意代表團晚到，「因為公理跟正義或許會遲到，但不會不到」。維特齊回應，盼這次行程可「為其他歐盟國家帶頭」，重申訪台沒違反布拉格與北京的外交協定，並以參議院名義邀請台灣立法院長游錫堃率團回訪，促進雙邊議會交流。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：TikTok交易 華暗示官方有發言權<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文在副總統賴清德等陪同下，上午在總統府大禮堂接見來訪的維特齊夫婦。她向今年1月病逝的柯佳洛追贈最高級別的「一。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RwBRkNurPWTMqVx9-eFDPiUfx2w=/4873x3248/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7VCMFQ7675DZNN6WTJLGSVWDKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRwBRkNurPWTMqVx9-eFDPiUfx2w%3D%2F4873x3248%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7VCMFQ7675DZNN6WTJLGSVWDKY.jpg&h=8d4a5369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蔡英文昨日在總統府接見維特齊。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n向病逝捷前議長追贈勳章<br />\n<br />\n談及維特齊日前提到，遺憾過去的參議院議長沒更早訪台，她說：「台灣人民並不介意各位的晚到，因為歷史經驗告訴我們，公理跟正義或許會遲到，但不會不到，只要堅持價值，台灣為民主自由所付出的努力，一定會被世界看見。」<br />\n<br />\n「台灣和捷克一樣，走過反抗威權、爭取民主自由的艱辛道路。我們以民主經驗為榮，也堅持守護民主防線，致力維護區域的和平、穩定和發展。」。。。<br />\n<br />\n維特齊表示，柯佳洛生前承諾訪台，整個參議院把他的生命理解為一種承諾，所以大。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eR_emiTc6g-rwiFfUZ5f6G_60VA=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UCTAUEVU6BGL3BLBFJCSQGUHA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeR_emiTc6g-rwiFfUZ5f6G_60VA%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUCTAUEVU6BGL3BLBFJCSQGUHA4.jpg&h=c79858e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蔡英文向捷克參議院前議長柯佳洛追頒「一等特種大綬卿雲勳章」，由維特齊代表接受。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反擊王毅：不喜歡這種表達<br />\n<br />\n維特齊下午與台灣外交部長吳釗燮舉行聯合記者會，雙方宣佈多天的交流已達成22項成果，包括由維特齊邀請游錫堃回訪捷克，台。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"3a2159ad43c5d8f475619393f7ebca3e16e9ad8a","tid":2188161,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"如果台積電訂單以訪台次序排... 應該會FULL BOOKING <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0602a915c7816f9b9b131036e94fbf1e6ff38e61","tid":2188161,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a2159ad43c5d8f475619393f7ebca3e16e9ad8a","tid":2188161,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"如果台積電訂單以訪台次序排... 應該會FULL BOOKING <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:45:24.000Z","msg":"好似富東閣片皮鴨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}